{"data":[{"id":563981137,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1fdfff23c7f2ddb81186d7ac9e8eff87","url_token":"freud-56-30","name":"Freud","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1fdfff23c7f2ddb81186d7ac9e8eff87","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":1,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563981137","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546317737,"updated_time":1546339307,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"comment_count":2,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e证明者勇敢的扩充质数定义，难道不是比大部分看笑话的并从这里找错误的人优秀？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们来看看他错在哪里。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在命题逻辑里，若p，则q（p→q）等价于非p或q，这是命题逻辑基础知识，可是证明者却错误的认为p→q等价于q\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e让我们来看看其证明过程。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果把 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 归到质数的集合中，可得命题：若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 是质数，则 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cforall%7Bn%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C2n%5Cin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"\\forall{n}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n\\in{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，且 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 为唯一的负质数。\u003cbr\u003e这个命题的逆否命题为：若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cexists%7Bn_0%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C2n_0%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"\\exists{n_0}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n_0\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，则 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 不是质数。\u003cbr\u003e当 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n_0%3D1\" alt=\"n_0=1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 时，若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"2\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，则 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 不是质数：这是一个真命题，所以该存在命题是真命题。\u003cbr\u003e由于原命题和其逆否命题具有等价关系，所以原命题是真命题，哥德巴赫猜想变式一正确。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e——引用提问连接中的内容\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们来将命题符号化：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1.根据其假设“-1是质数”（P），那么命题“则 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cforall%7Bn%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C2n%5Cin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"\\forall{n}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n\\in{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ”（∀nG（n），从3开始记为Q）就是所要证明的哥德巴赫猜想变式一。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2.由1，得命题P→∀nG（n）。在证明过程中其写成了逆否命题的形式“∃n┐G(n)→┐P”（存在n，若2n不属于A，则-1不是质数）。互为逆否命题是等价的命题，这里也看出来证明人只有高中的逻辑基础。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3.\u003cb\u003e关键错误在这：\u003c/b\u003e猜想认为\u003cb\u003e只要\u003c/b\u003eP→∀nG（n）\u003cb\u003e永真，\u003c/b\u003e那么哥德巴赫猜想变式一就成立，这是错误的。由1可知，\u003cb\u003eQ（\u003c/b\u003e∀nG（n）\u003cb\u003e）\u003c/b\u003e这个命题就是哥德巴赫猜想变式一，\u003cb\u003e（P→Q）→Q\u003c/b\u003e这样的推理显然是不成立的。举个\u003cb\u003e例子\u003c/b\u003e，\u003cb\u003e我要证明哥德巴赫猜想，\u003c/b\u003e设命题\u003cb\u003e“若地球是平的，则哥德巴赫猜想成立”，\u003c/b\u003e其逆否命题\u003cb\u003e“若哥德巴赫猜想不成立，地球是圆的”\u003c/b\u003e是真命题，所以原命题是真命题，所以我证出哥德巴赫猜想了？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e4：我们来看命题\u003cb\u003eP→Q\u003c/b\u003e什么情况下为\u003cb\u003e假\u003c/b\u003e：其\u003cb\u003e等价于\u003c/b\u003e┐P ∨ Q。我们知道只有当\u003cb\u003eP为真，Q为假\u003c/b\u003e时为假，其他情况都是真。那么如果\u003cb\u003eP永假，命题就是永真的了。所以这样的永真命题说明不了什么。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e临时手打，有错误或者符号不规范请大家见谅。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e我认为高中生限于眼界和知识做出一些错误的事情来是可以谅解的，而且勇敢的去思考和探索也是值得鼓励的。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个证明的思路是构造一个更加\u003cb\u003e高级的定理即哥德巴赫猜想变式，如果更高级的定理成立那么其低级一些的哥德巴赫猜想就成立，这思路是可行的，现实中很多定理也是这样证明的。我不是数学系的无法给出太多例子。但是类似的，就像柯西中值定理蕴含拉格朗日中值定理一样。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e我们应该多鼓励指导他，而不是冷嘲热讽。年少谁不轻狂，我们也只是过了不怕犯错的年纪而已……\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"证明者勇敢的扩充质数定义，难道不是比大部分看笑话的并从这里找错误的人优秀？我们来看看他错在哪里。在命题逻辑里，若p，则q（p→q）等价于非p或q，这是命题逻辑基础知识，可是证明者却错误的认为p→q等价于q让我们来看看其证明过程。如果把 -1 归到质数…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=227\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed